item.title: About
item.description: About Hey there, I’m a software developer from Portugal working on the Front-end side of applications. I enjoy solving software related problems and building open source tools. Work I’m currently working at MobieTrain a micro-learning platform as a Front-end developer. I enjoy the most working on complex application and systems. Contact I’m available for a chatting through LinkedIn and Twitter.
